    {
      "title": "Step Description Popup",
      "description": "# Step Description Popup\n\nStep\u0027s description is rendered on a popup modal dialog, which supports MARKDOWN/HTML rendering\n\nThe popup provides the following:\n\n- **Description** rendering with HTML support\n- **Resizable** and **Movable** panel as a popup modal\n- Adjustable **Font Size**\n- Buttons for navigating to Previous and Next Step\n\n**Tip**: *Shortcuts for navigating to Previous and Next Step are always active:*\n\n- Previous Step: **Ctrl+Alt+Q**\n- Next Step: **Ctrl+Alt+W**",
